</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="1B442A5C20C06FA1F0A03E825DA96668" pageId="0" pageNumber="95" type="phenology">
<paragraph id="CEED66ABDB5171198C764BCCAF5B8C35" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">Phenology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="89164345CAA7A201DA166FB17AB33AF4" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">Flowering occurs from May to early September, and fruiting from August to October.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="9C2B5B4981136E03FDB65F801C9B6664" pageId="0" pageNumber="95" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="2D7E12761A26F3D995FED231FEF2A228" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="38E603EB0C7FA237BA4062D3602EE5F6" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">
The specific epithet 
<taxonomicName id="72BB30134B676872814BB99FD1F997FB" authorityName="Huan C. Wang, Shao Y. Liu &amp; Z. T. Ren" authorityYear="2022" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Hemilophia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Hemilophia cardiocarpa" order="Brassicales" pageId="0" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cardiocarpa">
<emphasis id="AC84B234DF589592FFB2C2F546200338" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">Hemilophia cardiocarpa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is derived from the Greek words &quot; 
<emphasis id="96047696B828827C23D416D580DC4819" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">kardio</emphasis>
&quot; (heart) and &quot; 
<emphasis id="EDE1C736FBD7EC37EA0E9C546D751F68" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">karpos</emphasis>
&quot; (fruit), referring to the fruit shape of this new species.
</paragraph>
<caption id="C843540B81E46BDB00A818CB4975C1FE" doi="10.3897/phytokeys.194.82737.figure2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/673785" pageId="0" pageNumber="95" start="Figure 2" startId="F2">
<paragraph id="D05A4699D7F62BA961666CDF9B951D38" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">
<emphasis id="93C82F450EAF44ADEA2212B7C1568270" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">Figure 2.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="D26127B85CF60911651CE35274D61EB6" authorityName="Huan C. Wang, Shao Y. Liu &amp; Z. T. Ren" authorityYear="2022" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Hemilophia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Hemilophia cardiocarpa" order="Brassicales" pageId="0" pageNumber="95" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cardiocarpa">
<emphasis id="7CF4813333C31D179030C587EBC32EA5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="95">Hemilophia cardiocarpa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
